snippet: Paula Creamer moved into position to end a two-year victory drought, shooting a six-under-par 65 to take a two-stroke lead into the final round of the Kingsmill Championship in Williamsburg, Va.
abstract: Paula Creamer moves into position to end a two-year LPGA victory drought, shooting a six-under-par 65 to take a two-stroke lead into the final round of the Kingsmill Championship in Williamsburg, Va.
